name: Haveyouever
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: have you ever
des:
"Have you ever been in love?" , "Have you ever been heartbroken?", are you able to answer these embarrassing questions truthfully, if you can't this game ain't for you. 

You have to answer in yes or no, sounds easy right? So, let's begin your quest.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
